  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f832b14936fc2048824d9308b14ded6, type: 3}
  m_Name: AfterKurt
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  locationName: 
  locationBackground: {fileID: 0}
  allLines:
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1936918675910826544, guid: e8f1130d0e09cef45bb1f9ab49489848, type: 3}
    sentence: I have to ask, Linus. You seem like a fair, intelligent man. Yet you
      seem kind of stuck up on planetary stereotypes. Why is that the case?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dc24e77c8220d5b43bd418e911809b3b, type: 3}
    sentence: "Ah, you noticed. I really don\u2019t mean to be that way but I guess
      my job kind of revolves around stereotyping people in one way or another. I
      can\u2019t help but do the same in my day to day life."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "That\u2019s understandable, mine does too. But I sense something else
      underneath it. I mean, the way you speak-"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Are you psychoanalyzing me right now?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Ah maybe? I can\u2019t help myself either, it seems. I\u2019m not
      judging you for it, to be clear. I\u2019m just curious. You\u2019re.. interesting."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I\u2019m guessing you don\u2019t give out that compliment to anyone,
      huh?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I really don\u2019t, and it really is a compliment. You intrigue me."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Is that a good thing, though? Considering the context of our current
      situation...
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 
    eventTrigger: 
    choices:
    - choices: Most of the time, no.
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6dfcf49b9dbef5245a6e4fdfd433a4cd, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 1
      heartReward: 0
    - choices: Darling, romance is nothing if not intriguing.
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5e92f50991fcd624dbed9c8d6d7b5436, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0.5
      heartReward: 0
    - choices: It depends on whether I can truly trust you or not.
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ea76af41ffc48d9409ce4932e79b0ae2, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0
